General.Name: Monarch Casino & Resort Inc
General.Description: Monarch Casino & Resort, Inc., through its subsidiaries, owns and operates hotels and casinos. It owns and operates the Atlantis Casino Resort Spa in Reno, Nevada; and the Monarch Casino Resort Spa Black Hawk in Black Hawk, Colorado. The company also owns separate parcels of land. The company was incorporated in 1993 and is based in Reno, Nevada.
